      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! This beauty has been such a reliable companion for me and is still in really wonderful shape. It drives like a dream and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It\u2019s the perfect ride for someone looking for a dependable daily driver that still looks fantastic on the road. I'm sad to see it go, but I'd love for it to find a great new home. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all!",
