    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This power unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce 333 hp, delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the VANOS system has been professionally serviced to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The chassis benefits from a limited-slip M-Variable differential and an upgraded suspension geometry with Bilstein dampers, offering exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feel. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping consistent with road use, the drivetrain and cooling system are in peak operating condition, making this a mechanically superior example of a modern classic.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
