    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and daily utility. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection will reveal minor road peppering on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the upholstery is free of tears or stains, and all power features\u2014including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car has been treated with respect. It has a documented history of regular synthetic oil changes, and the most recent service included a fresh set of brake pads and a multi-point inspection. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts crisply without hesitation. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner to drive home today without any immediate maintenance concerns.",
      "price": 34800.0,
