      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and disciplined maintenance. This specimen has been rigorously vetted to ensure it meets our exacting standards for both performance and aesthetic presentation. It offers a refined driving experience, characterized by a well-preserved interior and a robust powertrain. For the discerning buyer seeking a balance of prestige and proven reliability, this offering represents an exceptional acquisition.",
