      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to go! It\u2019s been well-loved and is looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be appreciated just as much as I've enjoyed it. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
