    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS. This example delivers a visceral 8,000 RPM redline through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis has been maintained for structural longevity, including documented rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed cooling system. Power is managed via the factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip and turn-in response. While the exterior reflects honest road use, the drivetrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and new bushings to preserve the communicative feedback of the M-tuned suspension geometry.",
